Package org.lfj.lang.util

Class MemberSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfj.lang.util.MemberSpec
  • public class MemberSpec
extends java.lang.Object
    Member specs generalize the properties of both fields and methods. Fields are distinguished from methods by a flag and a lack of parameters. This defines the modifiers, name, and type data of the class member but not other attributes like the implementation.
